<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA31">
<l>aḻaku maṟivōmāy valviṉaiyum tīrppāṉ</l>
<l>niḻalu maṭitōṟu māṉōñ cuḻalak</l>
<l>kuṭaṅkaḷtalai mīteṭuttuk koṇṭāṭi yaṉṟat</l>
<l>taṭaṅkaṭalai mēyār tamakku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being such as know the beauty and the shade of each foot</l>
<l>of him who ends [our] harsh Karma, we have become</l>
<l>his, the one’s who resided on the vast ocean that day,</l>
<l>having danced with the pot lifted upon [his] head, so as to spin it.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
